CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE [dbo].[ext_FACT_INVENTSUM] WITH (
        LOCATION = 'FACT_INVENTSUM/Archive',
        DATA_SOURCE = [eds_tx-halfen-2-dwh],
        FILE_FORMAT = [eff_Parquet]
) AS
SELECT
    *
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK './FACT_INVENTSUM/In/2023/01/05/FACT_INVENTSUM_2023_01_05_05_01_32_204.parquet',
        FORMAT = 'PARQUET'
    ) AS [result]
WHERE DATAAREAID NOT IN ('5307', '5309', '5310', '5325')
